Repost from @conservationorg I’m super excited to be a part of this beautiful project. It is an honor. Mahalo @savethewavescoalition @surfconservation for protecting our waves Aloha j
—
“What do you think I can do to your currents, your coastlines, your climate? My requirements are simple. Stop stripping the forests that keep my water clean, stop filling the atmosphere with dead carbon and keep your plastic to yourself. Work with me now, before it’s too late. I’ll keep coming, I am the wave.”

Aquaman actor, Native Hawaiian and ocean sustainability advocate Jason Momoa (@prideofgypsies) joins Conservation International’s award-winning Nature is Speaking series as The Wave. #NatureisSpeaking

@savethewavescoalition @surfconservation @taylorsteele

node.text:
Repost from @totalfilm
•
Here’s an exclusive new look at sci-fi epic @dunemovie from our HUGE upcoming cover story.

Check out the new images - featuring @tchalamet, @zendaya, @officialrebeccaferguson, @joshbrolin, @bardemantarctic, Oscar Isaac and director Denis Villeneuve, and head to GamesRadar.com/totalfilm, for more on the new issue.

And check out the 20-page (!) feature when it hits shelves (and digital newsstands) this Friday!
